media:group.media:title: I wrote a children's book with my Instagram followers
media:group.media:description:
All of the drawings were done in photoshop using a drawing tablet and the brushes were from Kyle T Webster (if you're wondering).

This "story" was created using the answers from an Instagram story post. If you have a good story idea for the next installment comment it below.
